result.formatted_address: 223-227 Wan Chai Rd, Morrison Hill, Hong Kong
result.name: The Coffee Academics The Morrison

reviews.text:
You know you have great coffee when you go to Coffee Academics. This particular location has a very cool bicycle theme. 

Brunch is yummy. Staffs are friendly. Great atmosphere to chill, hangout or get some work done.

If you want breakfast with coffee go elsewhere. Came at a pretty non busy time and took 40 minutes for the avo on toast to come out. Had to ask after 30 minutes to get our coffees. Wasn’t worth the wait or price.  Nice staff though.

me and my wife walked in this place for a cup of tea without any prior info.

we had one seasonal special latte, iced tea, and a piece of lemon tart.

On latte, there were cream and melt-marshmellow which I liked. Fruits inthe iced tea were slightly torched so that it had richer flavor.

really liked these details and atmosphere and price-level were also satisfactory.

definitely visit again
Great coffee, but DOUBLE Starbucks price.  $45.00 for a simple cup of coffee.
Great coffee and a place to relax. Better than Starbucks as it’s more quiet. Good weekday lunch set (*one for one)!

reviews.text:
You know you have great coffee when you go to Coffee Academics. This particular location has a very cool bicycle theme. 

Brunch is yummy. Staffs are friendly. Great atmosphere to chill, hangout or get some work done.

價錢🔝
Agave, 黑胡椒咖啡😊👍
圖中兩杯咖啡, 黑胡椒粉唔夠. 飲唔出黑椒味
跟住換過第二杯, 咁先至係😊👍😋😍
服務都可以😊 因為換番兩杯咖啡👍👍👍
Brownies乾, 飲品世盃🏆, 仲貴過飲啤酒😅👍 大熱天時入嚟飲番杯, 真係兩啖已經冇了😏

If you want breakfast with coffee go elsewhere. Came at a pretty non busy time and took 40 minutes for the avo on toast to come out. Had to ask after 30 minutes to get our coffees. Wasn’t worth the wait or price.  Nice staff though.
今日真係好忙，接近3:00pm搵嘢食，諗都唔諗就想食黑松露長通粉，好好味！
以咖啡為主要產品之 cafe，水平可以，價格偏高。
